Extension: Imaging Settings

Official URL: https://build.fhir.org/ig/arkhn/arkhn-ig-osiris/StructureDefinition/imaging-settings Version: 2.1.0
Active as of 2023-03-28 Computable Name: ImagingSettings

Imaging Settings.

Context of Use

This extension may be used on the following element(s):

  • Element ID Element

Usage info

Usage:

  • Use this Extension: Imaging Study
  • Examples for this Extension: ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-ct, ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-dx, ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-mri-2, ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-mri and ImagingStudy/fhir-osiris-example-imagingstudy-pt-nm
